Calculate the standard entropy change for the following reaction:</p>
<div data-type="equation" id="fs-idp53679664"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mtext>Ca</mtext><msub><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mtext>OH</mtext><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mtext>s</mtext><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/><mo stretchy="false">&#10230;</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/><mtext>CaO</mtext><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><msub><mtext>H</mtext><mn>2</mn></msub><mtext>O</mtext><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>l</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mtext>Ca</mtext><msub><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mtext>OH</mtext><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mtext>s</mtext><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/><mo stretchy="false">&#10230;</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/><mtext>CaO</mtext><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>s</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><msub><mtext>H</mtext><mn>2</mn></msub><mtext>O</mtext><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>l</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></div>
